'From Squeak2.7 of 5 January 2000 [latest update: #1762] on 1 February 2000 at 3:43:55 pm'!"Change Set:		AEScriptFixDate:			1 February 2000Author:			Andreas RaabFixes an annoying problem with Applescript startup on non-Macs."!!Applescript class methodsFor: 'initialize-release' stamp: 'ar 2/1/2000 15:42'!startUp	Smalltalk platformName = 'Mac OS' "Can be *really* annoying otherwise"		ifTrue:[^self reopen]! !!SystemDictionary methodsFor: 'miscellaneous' stamp: 'ar 2/1/2000 15:39'!platformName	"Return the name of the platform we're running on"	^self getSystemAttribute: 1001! !